{"tid":166077,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"英媒指匯控渣打等銀行牽涉俄洗錢案","createTime":"2017-03-21T23:30:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T10:15:02.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"980e5d0177e84fa042bc638e268c07be7ceaa910","tid":166077,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T23:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://caiji.3g.cnfol.com/wine/images/201703/21/1490064722211416.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcaiji.3g.cnfol.com%2Fwine%2Fimages%2F201703%2F21%2F1490064722211416.jpg&h=7e412110&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國《衛報》報道，多間英國銀行牽涉大宗俄羅斯洗黑錢交易，經手了其中的將近7.4億美元。<br />\n<br />\n該報道引述由消息人士提供之文件指，洗黑錢網絡涉及英美兩地逾2,000間銀行機構及7萬宗交易，其中1,920間機構於英國注冊，另外373間則於美國。有關機構疑於2010-2014年間，自俄羅斯匯款逾200億美元，事件並牽涉俄羅斯總統普京的親屬Igor Putin，其為涉及有關洗黑錢事件之莫斯科銀行之董事會成員。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，匯控(<a href=\"http://00005.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00005.HK&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAcP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=9875df32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00005.HK</a>)  涉及當中5.45億美元金額交易，大部份經由本港分行渠道；另外渣打(<a href=\"http://02888.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F02888.HK&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAcP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=7c739cba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">02888.HK</a>)  、瑞銀、花旗、美銀、巴克萊及荷蘭國際集團等牽涉交易額則介乎200-3,700萬美元不等。銀行回應報道指內部有嚴格防洗黑錢措施，匯控發言人並指，有關事件反映私人企業及公眾間須有更多資訊公開，渣打則指若有證據顯示部份可疑交易違法，將進行調查。<br />\n<br />\n除以上銀行外，由英國政府持有71%股權之蘇格蘭皇家銀行及英女王亦為其客戶之一、於本港亦有提供服務的私人銀行顧資銀行亦涉及處理金額分別為1.13億美元及3,280萬美元交易。<br />\n<br />\n報道並指，處理洗黑錢手法包括企業之間互相借貸後違約，將有關金額自俄羅斯匯往摩爾多瓦後轉至拉脫維亞後轉至其他歐洲地區；亦有以龐大金額購買與申報商品不相稱之交易。摩爾多瓦及拉脫維亞兩地警方亦正調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cnfol.hk/news/gangguzx/20170321/24462963.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnfol.hk%2Fnews%2Fgangguzx%2F20170321%2F24462963.shtml&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAcP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=dd1a08d0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cnfol.hk/news/gangguzx/20170321/24462963.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"823a3b0109662e7a21c9f42c49019026dca4dd8e","tid":166077,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T23:36:53.000Z","msg":"又俾人罰錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf33759f45fff46214612a342446e8e1c84f31d","tid":166077,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T23:37:10.000Z","msg":"匯豐仲唔撚釘牌"},{"pid":"3f27304d372b847f6723b74a12da72fbe8bebe67","tid":166077,"uid":55990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T01:46:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68b336b8a57386e716769707a6dacc80a05741bf","tid":166077,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T03:56:01.000Z","msg":"點解間咁撚大的銀行成撚日都做D犯法野！<br />\n重要比人知道！"},{"pid":"955fd95ac5ec68c26f92af5c205915ee447c2994","tid":166077,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T06:45:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解間咁撚大的銀行成撚日都做D犯法野！<br />\n重要比人知道！</blockquote><br />\n最多咪罰錢,好過得失個大客,唔掂炒下啲港豬cut cost<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21830a4a7316ded1a1c658d14b38057cc903acd0","tid":166077,"uid":55990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T07:23:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dcb22815169656228cbef25333a2789b571fce26","tid":166077,"uid":53429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T08:18:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解間咁撚大的銀行成撚日都做D犯法野！<br />\n重要比人知道！</blockquote><br />\n最多咪罰錢,好過得失個大客,唔掂炒下啲港豬cut cost<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n炒IT狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPayme"},{"pid":"fdf33baac83077fda0785cfae33a5347c30078d1","tid":166077,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T10:15:02.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/